Topic: Zero Trust Principle

Objective:
1. Explain three principles of Zero Trust
2. Describe the benefits of the zero trust model in contrast to the perimeter network defense model
3. Describe some of the methods used to implement zero-trust security
###
Zero-trust security model is that trust must be explicitly derived from a mix of identity-based and context-based aspects

> Three Principles
1. Never trust, always verify
2. Implement least privilege
3. Assume your network is breached

